-h0sxub\"><div class=\"css-nj7ofv\">★这篇文章存在哪些缺陷？</div></div></div><div class=\"Catalog-SecondLevelTitle Catalog-Title css-1nds53c\"><div data-catalog-target-id=\"h_2363714796_22\" data-catalog-type=\"editor\" data-za-detail-view-id=\"9745\" data-za-detail-view-action=\"Click\" data-za-detail-view-name=\"正文\" class=\"css-h0sxub\"><div class=\"css-nj7ofv\">★作者关于这个课题的构思有哪几点？</div></div></div><div class=\"Catalog-SecondLevelTitle Catalog-Title css-1nds53c\"><div data-catalog-target-id=\"h_2363714796_23\" data-catalog-type=\"editor\" data-za-detail-view-id=\"9745\" data-za-detail-view-action=\"Click\" data-za-detail-view-name=\"正文\" class=\"css-h0sxub\"><div class=\"css-nj7ofv\">★未来可能的展望是什么？</div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><span id=\"content\"><span class=\"RichText ztext CopyrightRichText-richText css-10o75c2\" options=\"[object Object]\" itemprop=\"text\"><h2 data-first-child=\"\" id=\"h_2363714796_0\" data-into-catalog-status=\"\">科研萌新必备！</h2><div class=\"RichText-LinkCardContainer\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.zhihu.com/question/525934845/answer/2425918745\" data-draft-node=\"block\" data-draft-type=\"link-card\" data-text=\"考研拟录取后到研究生开学这段时间能做些什么？\" class=\"LinkCard new css-m92nl7\" data-image=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-2ba86b510aaa3d18a6c7ee13e9f5e475_180x120.jpg\" data-image-width=\"1400\" data-image-height=\"720\"><span class=\"LinkCard-image LinkCard-image--default\"></span><span class=\"LinkCard-contents\"><span class=\"LinkCard-title loading\" data-text=\"true\"></span><span class=\"LinkCard-desc loading\"></span></span></a></div><p data-pid=\"1qN45bPe\"><b>废话不多说，直接上文献阅读干货。</b></p><p data-pid=\"Ns-b4mxC\"><b>目录</b></p><blockquote data-pid=\"Xn9tL1Fy\"><b>一、<span><a class=\"RichContent-EntityWord css-b7erz1\" data-za-not-track-link=\"true\" data-paste-text=\"true\" href=\"https://zhida.zhihu.com/search?content_id=459848279&amp;content_type=Answer&amp;match_order=1&amp;q=%E6%96%87%E7%8C%AE%E7%AD%9B%E9%80%89&amp;zhida_source=entity\" target=\"_blank\">文献筛选<svg width=\"10px\" height=\"10px\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" class=\"ZDI ZDI--FourPointedStar16 css-1dvsrp\" fill=\"currentColor\"><path d=\"m5.068 9.267-3.08-.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0-.994l3.08-.77a2.289 2.289 0 0 0 1.665-1.665l.77-3.08a.512.512 0 0 1 .994 0l.77 3.08c.205.82.845 1.46 1.665 1.665l3.08.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0 .994l-3.08.77a2.29 2.29 0 0 0-1.665 1.665l-.77 3.08a.512.512 0 0 1-.994 0l-.77-3.08a2.289 2.289 0 0 0-1.665-1.665Z\"></path></svg></a></span></b><br><b>二、<span><a class=\"RichContent-EntityWord css-b7erz1\" data-za-not-track-link=\"true\" data-paste-text=\"true\" href=\"https://zhida.zhihu.com/search?content_id=459848279&amp;content_type=Answer&amp;match_order=1&amp;q=%E5%88%9B%E6%96%B0%E7%82%B9&amp;zhida_source=entity\" target=\"_blank\">创新点<svg width=\"10px\" height=\"10px\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" class=\"ZDI ZDI--FourPointedStar16 css-1dvsrp\" fill=\"currentColor\"><path d=\"m5.068 9.267-3.08-.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0-.994l3.08-.77a2.289 2.289 0 0 0 1.665-1.665l.77-3.08a.512.512 0 0 1 .994 0l.77 3.08c.205.82.845 1.46 1.665 1.665l3.08.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0 .994l-3.08.77a2.29 2.29 0 0 0-1.665 1.665l-.77 3.08a.512.512 0 0 1-.994 0l-.77-3.08a2.289 2.289 0 0 0-1.665-1.665Z\"></path></svg></a></span></b><br><b>三、<span><a class=\"RichContent-EntityWord css-b7erz1\" data-za-not-track-link=\"true\" data-paste-text=\"true\" href=\"https://zhida.zhihu.com/search?content_id=459848279&amp;content_type=Answer&amp;match_order=1&amp;q=%E6%96%87%E7%8C%AE%E9%98%85%E8%AF%BB%E6%96%B9%E6%B3%95&amp;zhida_source=entity\" target=\"_blank\">文献阅读方法<svg width=\"10px\" height=\"10px\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" class=\"ZDI ZDI--FourPointedStar16 css-1dvsrp\" fill=\"currentColor\"><path d=\"m5.068 9.267-3.08-.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0-.994l3.08-.77a2.289 2.289 0 0 0 1.665-1.665l.77-3.08a.512.512 0 0 1 .994 0l.77 3.08c.205.82.845 1.46 1.665 1.665l3.08.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0 .994l-3.08.77a2.29 2.29 0 0 0-1.665 1.665l-.77 3.08a.512.512 0 0 1-.994 0l-.77-3.08a2.289 2.289 0 0 0-1.665-1.665Z\"></path></svg></a></span></b></blockquote><h2 id=\"h_2363714796_1\" data-into-catalog-status=\"\">一、文献筛选</h2><h2 id=\"h_2363714796_2\" data-into-catalog-status=\"\">第1步</h2><p data-pid=\"oVHFKqGK\">读标题和关键词推测这篇论文的大致主题和内容，以此判断自己是否感兴趣或者是否需要，如果答案是“否”，那就舍弃这篇论文。</p><h2 id=\"h_2363714796_3\" data-into-catalog-status=\"\">第2步</h2><p data-pid=\"eoauQJ4a\">读摘要，摘要会说明论文的基本内容、方法特色、主要贡献，是整篇论文内容的浓缩，非常重要。多数论文看摘要，少数论文看全文。如果从摘要判断这篇文章不是你想要的，即刻舍弃。</p><h2 id=\"h_2363714796_4\" data-into-catalog-status=\"\">第3步</h2><p data-pid=\"KcbCbKEP\">跳过前言、实验方法等部分，直接看作者得出的结论，如果结论和你不是很相关，同样地舍弃这篇论文。</p><div class=\"RichText-LinkCardContainer\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//www.bilibili.com/video/BV1U3411z7z4%3Fshare_source%3Dcopy_web\" data-draft-node=\"block\" data-draft-type=\"link-card\" data-text=\"【研究生】手把手教你阅读一篇英文文献｜绝对够干，一滴都没有了_哔哩哔哩_bilibili\" class=\"LinkCard new css-m92nl7\" data-image=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-e37b66d76102230f79a7ad6c0de0b705_180x120.jpg\" data-image-width=\"781\" data-image-height=\"489\"><span class=\"LinkCard-image LinkCard-image--default\"></span><span class=\"LinkCard-contents\"><span class=\"LinkCard-title loading\" data-text=\"true\"></span><span class=\"LinkCard-desc loading\"></span></span></a></div><h2 id=\"h_2363714796_5\" data-into-catalog-status=\"\">二、创新点</h2><p data-pid=\"7BaTu9b1\">对于任何一篇文章来说，最重要的就是这篇文章的创新点。一般来说创新点的出现位置在<span><a class=\"RichContent-EntityWord css-b7erz1\" data-za-not-track-link=\"true\" data-paste-text=\"true\" href=\"https://zhida.zhihu.com/search?content_id=459848279&amp;content_type=Answer&amp;match_order=1&amp;q=Abstract&amp;zhida_source=entity\" target=\"_blank\">Abstract<svg width=\"10px\" height=\"10px\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" class=\"ZDI ZDI--FourPointedStar16 css-1dvsrp\" fill=\"currentColor\"><path d=\"m5.068 9.267-3.08-.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0-.994l3.08-.77a2.289 2.289 0 0 0 1.665-1.665l.77-3.08a.512.512 0 0 1 .994 0l.77 3.08c.205.82.845 1.46 1.665 1.665l3.08.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0 .994l-3.08.77a2.29 2.29 0 0 0-1.665 1.665l-.77 3.08a.512.512 0 0 1-.994 0l-.77-3.08a2.289 2.289 0 0 0-1.665-1.665Z\"></path></svg></a></span>结尾部分、Introduction结尾部分以及Conclusions结尾部分甚至有些直接会出现在题目中</p><p data-pid=\"I2Xf1TeD\">以下面这篇文章为例</p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-ab5e27619bd93532660ca16eeea7f113_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"1036\" data-rawheight=\"406\" data-original-token=\"v2-a3b612716ba5e057812676225d6f09ea\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-291ebf426bf1dd5a347a0bf5af75812f_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1036\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-ab5e27619bd93532660ca16eeea7f113_r.jpg?source=1def8aca\"/></noscript><div><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,<svg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='1036' height='406'></svg>\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"1036\" data-rawheight=\"406\" data-original-token=\"v2-a3b612716ba5e057812676225d6f09ea\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-291ebf426bf1dd5a347a0bf5af75812f_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1036\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-ab5e27619bd93532660ca16eeea7f113_r.jpg?source=1def8aca\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-ab5e27619bd93532660ca16eeea7f113_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\"></div></figure><h3 id=\"h_2363714796_6\" data-into-catalog-status=\"\">Abstract结尾部分</h3><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-9c18267d60708bb6f9f8dde5e7825e78_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"704\" data-rawheight=\"60\" data-original-token=\"v2-9c18267d60708bb6f9f8dde5e7825e78\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"704\" data-original=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/v2-9c18267d60708bb6f9f8dde5e7825e78_r.jpg?source=1def8aca\"/></noscript><div><img src=\"data: