</svg>\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"482\" data-rawheight=\"79\" data-original-token=\"v2-2b879e232a81e8fd363e9cf34fece30e\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"482\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-2b879e232a81e8fd363e9cf34fece30e_r.jpg?source=1def8aca\" data-actualsrc=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-2b879e232a81e8fd363e9cf34fece30e_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\"></div></figure><h3 id=\"h_2363714796_16\" data-into-catalog-status=\"\">★作者是如何解决这些问题的？使用的理论是基于哪些假设？</h3><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-ed62eb901ef42d1d68fae7450f033997_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"476\" data-rawheight=\"312\" data-original-token=\"v2-e8d3aa101c55af63ac2bd68ccefd6aaf\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-36c3ec396be7e1afff99fbe6f5edf5ea_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"476\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-ed62eb901ef42d1d68fae7450f033997_r.jpg?source=1def8aca\"/></noscript><div><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,<svg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='476' height='312'></svg>\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"476\" data-rawheight=\"312\" data-original-token=\"v2-e8d3aa101c55af63ac2bd68ccefd6aaf\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-36c3ec396be7e1afff99fbe6f5edf5ea_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"476\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-ed62eb901ef42d1d68fae7450f033997_r.jpg?source=1def8aca\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-ed62eb901ef42d1d68fae7450f033997_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\"></div></figure><h3 id=\"h_2363714796_17\" data-into-catalog-status=\"\">★作者在这篇文章中具体做了什么？</h3><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-d8bcd8c2bf5b3303df1637dedc5a2627_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" 